# 简介：

# 【1月份拍摄】我是雪鱼，带你一起踏上寻味之旅。广东佛山，到处可见牛杂小吃摊，经过多方了解，才知道同济牌坊（地名）的牛杂口碑最好。售卖牛杂的小摊已经快40年，现在是一对夫妻经营，大锅的牛杂冒着热气，上面是黄色的豆腐泡，经过这里的时候就会闻到飘过来的香气，让人忍不住停下脚步，来品尝它的味道。花了50元买了一盘，卤汁、辣椒酱、大块牛杂，端着坐在公园的小路上吃，感觉幸福极了。

# [Video shot in January 2020] I'm Xueyu on a journey searching for the best flavor. In Foshan, Guangdong, beef offal shops can be seen anywhere. As many people may agree, the beef offal shop in Tongji Paifang is the most popular. This shop has been selling beef offal for nearly 40 years and is now being run by a couple. The beef offal is boiled in a giant pot together with fried tofu on the top, releasing an irresistible aroma that attracts a lot of customers. I spent 50 yuan for one plate of beef offal, which was served with broth and chili sauce. Life is just fantastic when you enjoy large pieces of beef offal while sitting along a small path in a park.

